a grape-vine to rise upon it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elevated structure upon which a grape-vine spreads itself:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaraAy^i$u","text_ar":"عَرَايِشُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, Msb,) [and perhaps"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiraA$N","text_ar":"عِرَاشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also: see 8.] ―         -b3-  Also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eariy$N","text_ar":"عَرِيشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing resembling a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hawodaj","text_ar":"هَوْدَج"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but not"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exactly the same as"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, made for a woman, who sits in it upon her camel:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) so called as being likened in form to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ery$","text_ar":"عريش"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a vine: (Er-Rághib:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eariy$apN","text_ar":"عَرِيشَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hwdj","text_ar":"هودج"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and its pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaraAy^i$u","text_ar":"عَرَايِشُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) which signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hawaAdiju","text_ar":"هَوَادِجُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (ISh, A.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An enclosure of the kind called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaZiyrap","text_ar":"حَظِيرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made for beasts, to protect them from the cold."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","S","Mgh","Msb","O"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}